{
 "name": "RPlog_Kashyyyk_Infiltration",
 "title": "Kashyyyk Infiltration",
 "summary": "Danik Kreldin delivers a platoon of Imperial infantry under Corporal Whorus to the jungle world of Kashyyyk to raid a New Republic communications array, accompanied by the dark-touched BofO Director Petra Doom and Major Anatoli Black. As the Imperials infiltrate the canopy, New Republic forces scramble: drop-pod marines including Savine Wolfray, Yarah Ravenlocke, and PFC Bastirio plummet planetward while Wookiee defenders Nol'Fet and Rharkyrtha stalk the intruders. The two forces converge on the array, and a Wookiee's ambush of the Imperial rear guard touches off a sprawling firefight. As the marine skirmish line is surrounded and cut down, the Imperial vanguard presses on unimpeded toward its target.",
